	<h1 class="title">看过《单身男子》，怎会不想了解 Tom Ford 的电影美学？| 电影时尚</h1>
	<div class="author-date clearfix">					
			<div class="author clearfix">
					<span class="avatar x25 circle">
						<img src="/img/missing_face.png" alt="">
					</span>
				<span class="name">Grace</span>
			</div>
		<span class="date smart-date" data-originDate="2015-12-13 08:45:04 +0800"></span>
	</div>
	<div class="banner">
			<img src="/system/articles/articleshows/18954/medium/18954.jpg?1449896229" alt="" />			
	</div>
	<!-- 传入参数：obj(aritcle, paper, card, mob) -->


<div class="com-share" data-id="18954" data-title="《看过《单身男子》，怎会不想了解 Tom Ford 的电影美学？| 电影时尚》，来自@好奇心日报" data-pic="http://www.qdaily.com/system/articles/articleshows/18954/medium/18954.jpg?1449896229" data-url="http://www.qdaily.com/mobile/articles/18954.html?from=timeline&amp;isappinstalled=1" data-weiboAppkey="2462590045">
